org.openpnp.machine.reference.driver

Class NullDriver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openpnp.machine.reference.driver.NullDriver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable, ReferenceDriver, PropertySheetHolder, WizardConfigurable

    public class NullDriver
extends java.lang.Object
implements ReferenceDriver
    An example of the simplest possible driver that can support multiple heads. This driver maintains a set of coordinates for each Head that it is asked to handle and simply logs all commands sent to it.
